HEADWORD: Decuple
<hw>Dec"u*ple</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A number ten times
repeated.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Decuple</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Decuple
